<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to GreenFields FPO</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:700,400&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Montserrat", Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a8e063 0%, #56ab2f 100%);
        color: #222;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .top-bar {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        background: transparent;
        padding: 12px 32px 0 32px;
      }

      .menu-toggle {
        font-size: 24px;
        background: none;
        border: none;
        color: #388e3c;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: none;
      }

      .auth-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .auth-links a {
        background: #fff;
        color: #388e3c;
        border: 2px solid #388e3c;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 7px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
      }

      .auth-links a:hover {
        background: #388e3c;
        color: #fff;
      }

      header {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
        padding: 30px 0 20px 0;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
      }

      header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        color: #388e3c;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
      }

      header p {
        margin: 10px 0 0 0;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #555;
      }

      nav {
        margin: 30px 0 0 0;
        text-align: center;
        display: block;
      }

      nav a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 0 18px;
        padding: 10px 22px;
        background: #388e3c;
        color: #fff;
        border-radius: 25px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        transition: background 0.2s;
      }

      nav a:hover {
        background: #2e7031;
      }

      .hero {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        margin: 60px 0 40px 0;
        padding: 0 16px;
      }

      .hero img {
        width: 220px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(56, 142, 60, 0.15);
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .hero h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #2e7031;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .hero p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #444;
        max-width: 600px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .features {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 30px;
        margin: 50px 0;
        padding: 0 16px;
      }

      .feature-card {
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 18px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(56, 142, 60, 0.09);
        padding: 30px 24px;
        width: 290px;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.2s;
      }

      .feature-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.03);
      }

      .feature-card img {
        width: 60px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      .feature-card h3 {
        color: #388e3c;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .feature-card p {
        color: #555;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      footer {
        background: #388e3c;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 18px 0;
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      /* Responsive Styles */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .menu-toggle {
          display: block;
        }

        nav {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          margin-top: 20px;
        }

        nav a {
          margin: 10px auto;
        }

        .top-bar {
          flex-direction: row;
          justify-content: space-between;
          align-items: center;
        }

        .auth-links {
          flex-shrink: 0;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="top-bar">
      <button
        class="menu-toggle"
        onclick="document.querySelector('nav').classList.toggle('show')"
      >
        ‚ò∞
      </button>
      <div class="auth-links">
        <a href="/login">Login</a>
        <a href="/signup">Sign Up</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <header>
      <h1>Sugam Uday Krishi Haat</h1>
      <p>Empowering Farmers. Growing Together.</p>
      <nav class="show">
        <a href="/aboutus">About Us</a>
        <a href="/services">Services</a>
        <a href="/members">Members</a>
        <a href="/contact">ContactUs</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506744038136-46273834b3fb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80"
        alt="Farmers working in field"
      />
      <h2>Welcome to Sugam Uday Krishi Haat</h2>
      <p>
        Sugam Uday Krishi Haat(Sukhüöúüåæüë®‚Äçüåæ) is dedicated to supporting and
        uplifting farmers by providing access to modern agricultural practices,
        fair markets, and community-driven growth. Join us in our mission to
        create a sustainable and prosperous future for all farmers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <img
          src="https://img.icons8.com/color/96/000000/tractor.png"
          alt="Modern Farming"
        />
        <h3>Modern Farming</h3>
        <p>
          Adopt the latest techniques and equipment for higher yields and
          sustainable agriculture.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <img
          src="https://img.icons8.com/color/96/000000/market-square.png"
          alt="Market Access"
        />
        <h3>Market Access</h3>
        <p>
          Connect directly with buyers and get the best prices for your produce
          through our network.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <img
          src="https://img.icons8.com/color/96/000000/handshake.png"
          alt="Community Support"
        />
        <h3>Community Support</h3>
        <p>
          Benefit from training, workshops, and a strong community of fellow
          farmers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      &copy; <span id="year"></span> GreenFields FPO. All rights reserved.
    </footer>

    <script>
      document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
